{"thi-ap19:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap19:0.2":"Ekuposathikavagga ","thi-ap19:0.3":"Uppalavannatheriapadana ","thi-ap19:1.1":"“Bhikkhuni uppalavanna, ","thi-ap19:1.2":"iddhiya paramim gata; ","thi-ap19:1.3":"Vanditva satthuno pade, ","thi-ap19:1.4":"idam vacanamabravi. ","thi-ap19:2.1":"‘Nitthinna jatisamsaram, ","thi-ap19:2.2":"pattaham acalam padam; ","thi-ap19:2.3":"Sabbadukkham maya khinam, ","thi-ap19:2.4":"arocemi mahamuni. ","thi-ap19:3.1":"Yavata parisa atthi, ","thi-ap19:3.2":"pasanna jinasasane; ","thi-ap19:3.3":"Yassa ca meparadhotthi, ","thi-ap19:3.4":"khamantu jinasammukha. ","thi-ap19:4.1":"Samsare samsarantiya, ","thi-ap19:4.2":"khalitam me sace bhave; ","thi-ap19:4.3":"Arocemi mahavira, ","thi-ap19:4.4":"aparadham khamassu tam’. ","thi-ap19:5.1":"‘Iddhincapi nidassehi, ","thi-ap19:5.2":"mama sasanakarike; ","thi-ap19:5.3":"Catasso parisa ajja, ","thi-ap19:5.4":"kankham chindahi yavata’. ","thi-ap19:6.1":"‘Dhita tuyham mahavira, ","thi-ap19:6.2":"pannavanta jutindhara; ","thi-ap19:6.3":"Bahunca dukkaram kammam, ","thi-ap19:6.4":"katam me atidukkaram. ","thi-ap19:7.1":"Uppalasseva me vanno, ","thi-ap19:7.2":"namenuppalanamika; ","thi-ap19:7.3":"Savika te mahavira, ","thi-ap19:7.4":"pade vandami cakkhuma. ","thi-ap19:8.1":"Rahulo ca ahanceva, ","thi-ap19:8.2":"nekajatisate bahu; ","thi-ap19:8.3":"Ekasmim sambhave jata, ","thi-ap19:8.4":"samanachandamanasa. ","thi-ap19:9.1":"Nibbatti ekato hoti, ","thi-ap19:9.2":"jatiyapi ca ekato; ","thi-ap19:9.3":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","thi-ap19:9.4":"ubhopi nanasambhava. ","thi-ap19:10.1":"Putto ca rahulo nama, ","thi-ap19:10.2":"dhita uppalasavhaya; ","thi-ap19:10.3":"Passa vira mamam iddhim, ","thi-ap19:10.4":"balam dassemi satthuno’. ","thi-ap19:11.1":"Mahasamudde caturo, ","thi-ap19:11.2":"pakkhipi hatthapatiyam; ","thi-ap19:11.3":"Telam hatthagatanceva, ","thi-ap19:11.4":"khiddo komarako yatha. ","thi-ap19:12.1":"Ubbattayitva pathavim, ","thi-ap19:12.2":"pakkhipi hatthapatiyam; ","thi-ap19:12.3":"Cittam munjam yatha nama, ","thi-ap19:12.4":"lunci komarako yuva. ","thi-ap19:13.1":"Cakkavalasamam panim, ","thi-ap19:13.2":"chadayitvana matthake; ","thi-ap19:13.3":"Vassapetvana phusitam, ","thi-ap19:13.4":"nanavannam punappunam. ","thi-ap19:14.1":"Bhumim udukkhalam katva, ","thi-ap19:14.2":"dhannam katvana sakkharam; ","thi-ap19:14.3":"Sinerum musalam katva, ","thi-ap19:14.4":"maddi komarika yatha. ","thi-ap19:15.1":"‘Dhitaham buddhasetthassa, ","thi-ap19:15.2":"namenuppalasavhaya; ","thi-ap19:15.3":"Abhinnasu vasibhuta, ","thi-ap19:15.4":"tava sasanakarika. ","thi-ap19:16.1":"Nanavikubbanam katva, ","thi-ap19:16.2":"dassetva lokanayakam; ","thi-ap19:16.3":"Namagottanca savetva, ","thi-ap19:16.4":"pade vandami cakkhuma. ","thi-ap19:17.1":"Iddhisu ca vasi homi, ","thi-ap19:17.2":"dibbaya sotadhatuya; ","thi-ap19:17.3":"Cetopariyananassa, ","thi-ap19:17.4":"vasi homi mahamune. ","thi-ap19:18.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thi-ap19:18.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thi-ap19:18.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","thi-ap19:18.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thi-ap19:19.1":"Atthadhammaniruttisu, ","thi-ap19:19.2":"Patibhane tatheva ca; ","thi-ap19:19.3":"Nanam me vimalam suddham, ","thi-ap19:19.4":"Sabhavena mahesino. ","thi-ap19:20.1":"Purimanam jinagganam, ","thi-ap19:20.2":"sangamam te nidassitam; ","thi-ap19:20.3":"Adhikaram bahum mayham, ","thi-ap19:20.4":"tuyhatthaya mahamuni. ","thi-ap19:21.1":"Yam maya puritam kammam, ","thi-ap19:21.2":"Kusalam sara me muni; ","thi-ap19:21.3":"Tavatthaya mahavira, ","thi-ap19:21.4":"Punnam upacitam maya. ","thi-ap19:22.1":"Abhabbatthane vajjetva, ","thi-ap19:22.2":"varayanti anacaram; ","thi-ap19:22.3":"Tavatthaya mahavira, ","thi-ap19:22.4":"cattam me jivituttamam. ","thi-ap19:23.1":"Dasakotisahassani, ","thi-ap19:23.2":"adasim mama jivitam; ","thi-ap19:23.3":"Pariccatta ca me homi, ","thi-ap19:23.4":"tavatthaya mahamuni’. ","thi-ap19:24.1":"Tadativimhita sabba, ","thi-ap19:24.2":"sirasava katanjali; ","thi-ap19:24.3":"‘Avocayye katham asi, ","thi-ap19:24.4":"atuliddhiparakkama’. ","thi-ap19:25.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","thi-ap19:25.2":"nagakanna aham tada; ","thi-ap19:25.3":"Vimala nama namena, ","thi-ap19:25.4":"kannanam sadhusammata. ","thi-ap19:26.1":"Mahorago mahanago, ","thi-ap19:26.2":"pasanno jinasasane; ","thi-ap19:26.3":"Padumuttaram mahatejam, ","thi-ap19:26.4":"nimantesi sasavakam. ","thi-ap19:27.1":"Ratanamayam mandapam, ","thi-ap19:27.2":"pallankam ratanamayam; ","thi-ap19:27.3":"Ratanam valukakinnam, ","thi-ap19:27.4":"upabhogam ratanamayam. ","thi-ap19:28.1":"Magganca patiyadesi, ","thi-ap19:28.2":"ratanaddhajabhusitam; ","thi-ap19:28.3":"Paccuggantvana sambuddham, ","thi-ap19:28.4":"vajjanto turiyehi so. ","thi-ap19:29.1":"Parisahi ca catuhi, ","thi-ap19:29.2":"parivuto lokanayako; ","thi-ap19:29.3":"Mahoragassa bhavane, ","thi-ap19:29.4":"nisidi paramasane. ","thi-ap19:30.1":"Annam panam khadaniyam, ","thi-ap19:30.2":"bhojananca maharaham; ","thi-ap19:30.3":"Varam varanca padasi, ","thi-ap19:30.4":"nagaraja mahayasam. ","thi-ap19:31.1":"Bhunjitvana sambuddho, ","thi-ap19:31.2":"pattam dhovitva yoniso; ","thi-ap19:31.3":"Anumodaniyankasi, ","thi-ap19:31.4":"nagakanna mahiddhika. ","thi-ap19:32.1":"Sabbannum phullitam disva, ","thi-ap19:32.2":"nagakanna mahayasam; ","thi-ap19:32.3":"Pasannam satthuno cittam, ","thi-ap19:32.4":"sunibandhanca manasam. ","thi-ap19:33.1":"Mamanca cittamannaya, ","thi-ap19:33.2":"jalajuttamanamako; ","thi-ap19:33.3":"Tasmim khane mahaviro, ","thi-ap19:33.4":"bhikkhunim dassayiddhiya. ","thi-ap19:34.1":"Iddhi aneka dassesi, ","thi-ap19:34.2":"bhikkhuni sa visarada; ","thi-ap19:34.3":"Pamodita vedajata, ","thi-ap19:34.4":"sattharam idamabravi. ","thi-ap19:35.1":"‘Addasaham imam iddhim, ","thi-ap19:35.2":"sumanam itarayapi; ","thi-ap19:35.3":"Katham ahosi sa vira, ","thi-ap19:35.4":"iddhiya suvisarada’. ","thi-ap19:36.1":"‘Orasa mukhato jata, ","thi-ap19:36.2":"dhita mama mahiddhika; ","thi-ap19:36.3":"Mamanusasanikara, ","thi-ap19:36.4":"iddhiya suvisarada’. ","thi-ap19:37.1":"Buddhassa vacanam sutva, ","thi-ap19:37.2":"evam patthesaham tada; ","thi-ap19:37.3":"‘Ahampi tadisa homi, ","thi-ap19:37.4":"iddhiya suvisarada. ","thi-ap19:38.1":"Pamoditaham sumana, ","thi-ap19:38.2":"patthe uttamamanasa; ","thi-ap19:38.3":"Anagatamhi addhane, ","thi-ap19:38.4":"idisa homi nayaka’. ","thi-ap19:39.1":"Manimayamhi pallanke, ","thi-ap19:39.2":"mandapamhi pabhassare; ","thi-ap19:39.3":"Annapanena tappetva, ","thi-ap19:39.4":"sasangham lokanayakam. ","thi-ap19:40.1":"Naganam pavaram puppham, ","thi-ap19:40.2":"arunam nama uppalam; ","thi-ap19:40.3":"‘Vannam me idisam hotu’, ","thi-ap19:40.4":"pujesim lokanayakam. ","thi-ap19:41.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap19:41.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap19:41.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap19:41.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap19:42.1":"Tato cutaham manuje, ","thi-ap19:42.2":"upapanna sayambhuno; ","thi-ap19:42.3":"Uppalehi paticchannam, ","thi-ap19:42.4":"pindapatamadasaham. ","thi-ap19:43.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","thi-ap19:43.2":"vipassi nama nayako; ","thi-ap19:43.3":"Uppajji carudassano, ","thi-ap19:43.4":"sabbadhammesu cakkhuma. ","thi-ap19:44.1":"Setthidhita tada hutva, ","thi-ap19:44.2":"baranasipuruttame; ","thi-ap19:44.3":"Nimantetvana sambuddham, ","thi-ap19:44.4":"sasangham lokanayakam. ","thi-ap19:45.1":"Mahadanam daditvana, ","thi-ap19:45.2":"uppalehi vinayakam; ","thi-ap19:45.3":"Pujayitva cetasava, ","thi-ap19:45.4":"vannasobham apatthayim. ","thi-ap19:46.1":"Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","thi-ap19:46.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","thi-ap19:46.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","thi-ap19:46.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","thi-ap19:47.1":"Upatthako mahesissa, ","thi-ap19:47.2":"tada asi narissaro; ","thi-ap19:47.3":"Kasiraja kiki nama, ","thi-ap19:47.4":"baranasipuruttame. ","thi-ap19:48.1":"Tassasim dutiya dhita, ","thi-ap19:48.2":"samanaguttasavhaya; ","thi-ap19:48.3":"Dhammam sutva jinaggassa, ","thi-ap19:48.4":"pabbajjam samarocayim. ","thi-ap19:49.1":"Anujani na no tato, ","thi-ap19:49.2":"agareva tada mayam; ","thi-ap19:49.3":"Visavassasahassani, ","thi-ap19:49.4":"vicarimha atandita. ","thi-ap19:50.1":"Komaribrahmacariyam, ","thi-ap19:50.2":"rajakanna sukhedhita; ","thi-ap19:50.3":"Buddhopatthananirata, ","thi-ap19:50.4":"mudita sattadhitaro. ","thi-ap19:51.1":"Samani samanagutta ca, ","thi-ap19:51.2":"bhikkhuni bhikkhudayika; ","thi-ap19:51.3":"Dhamma ceva sudhamma ca, ","thi-ap19:51.4":"sattami sanghadayika. ","thi-ap19:52.1":"Aham khema ca sappanna, ","thi-ap19:52.2":"patacara ca kundala; ","thi-ap19:52.3":"Kisagotami dhammadinna, ","thi-ap19:52.4":"visakha hoti sattami. ","thi-ap19:53.1":"Tehi kammehi sukatehi, ","thi-ap19:53.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap19:53.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap19:53.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap19:54.1":"Tato cuta manussesu, ","thi-ap19:54.2":"upapanna mahakule; ","thi-ap19:54.3":"Pitam mattham varam dussam, ","thi-ap19:54.4":"adam arahato aham. ","thi-ap19:55.1":"Tato cutaritthapure, ","thi-ap19:55.2":"jata vippakule aham; ","thi-ap19:55.3":"Dhita tiritivacchassa, ","thi-ap19:55.4":"ummadanti manohara. ","thi-ap19:56.1":"Tato cuta janapade, ","thi-ap19:56.2":"kule annatare aham; ","thi-ap19:56.3":"Pasuta natiphitamhi, ","thi-ap19:56.4":"salim gopemaham tada. ","thi-ap19:57.1":"Disva paccekasambuddham, ","thi-ap19:57.2":"pancalajasataniham; ","thi-ap19:57.3":"Datva padumacchannani, ","thi-ap19:57.4":"panca puttasataniham. ","thi-ap19:58.1":"Patthayim tepi patthesum, ","thi-ap19:58.2":"madhum datva sayambhuno; ","thi-ap19:58.3":"Tato cuta aranneham, ","thi-ap19:58.4":"ajayim padumodare. ","thi-ap19:59.1":"Kasiranno mahesiham, ","thi-ap19:59.2":"hutva sakkatapujita; ","thi-ap19:59.3":"Ajanim rajaputtanam, ","thi-ap19:59.4":"anunam satapancakam. ","thi-ap19:60.1":"Yada te yobbanappatta, ","thi-ap19:60.2":"kilanta jalakilitam; ","thi-ap19:60.3":"Disva opattapadumam, ","thi-ap19:60.4":"asum paccekanayaka. ","thi-ap19:61.1":"Saham tehi vinabhuta, ","thi-ap19:61.2":"sutavirehi sokini; ","thi-ap19:61.3":"Cuta isigilipasse, ","thi-ap19:61.4":"gamakamhi ajayiham. ","thi-ap19:62.1":"Yada buddha sutamati, ","thi-ap19:62.2":"sutanam bhattunopi ca; ","thi-ap19:62.3":"Yagum adaya gacchanti, ","thi-ap19:62.4":"attha paccekanayake. ","thi-ap19:63.1":"Bhikkhaya gamam gacchante, ","thi-ap19:63.2":"disva putte anussarim; ","thi-ap19:63.3":"Khiradhara viniggacchi, ","thi-ap19:63.4":"tada me puttapemasa. ","thi-ap19:64.1":"Tato tesam adam yagum, ","thi-ap19:64.2":"pasanna sehi panibhi; ","thi-ap19:64.3":"Tato cutaham tidasam, ","thi-ap19:64.4":"nandanam upapajjaham. ","thi-ap19:65.1":"Anubhotva sukham dukkham, ","thi-ap19:65.2":"samsaritva bhavabhave; ","thi-ap19:65.3":"Tavatthaya mahavira, ","thi-ap19:65.4":"pariccattanca jivitam. ","thi-ap19:66.1":"Evam bahuvidham dukkham, ","thi-ap19:66.2":"sampatti ca bahubbidha; ","thi-ap19:66.3":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","thi-ap19:66.4":"jata savatthiyam pure. ","thi-ap19:67.1":"Mahadhanasetthikule, ","thi-ap19:67.2":"sukhite sajjite tatha; ","thi-ap19:67.3":"Nanaratanapajjote, ","thi-ap19:67.4":"sabbakamasamiddhine. ","thi-ap19:68.1":"Sakkata pujita ceva, ","thi-ap19:68.2":"manitapacita tatha; ","thi-ap19:68.3":"Rupasobhaggasampanna, ","thi-ap19:68.4":"kulesu atisakkata. ","thi-ap19:69.1":"Ativa patthita casim, ","thi-ap19:69.2":"rupabhogasirihi ca; ","thi-ap19:69.3":"Patthita setthiputtehi, ","thi-ap19:69.4":"anekehi satehipi. ","thi-ap19:70.1":"Agaram pajahitvana, ","thi-ap19:70.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","thi-ap19:70.3":"Addhamase asampatte, ","thi-ap19:70.4":"catusaccamapapunim. ","thi-ap19:71.1":"Iddhiya abhinimmitva, ","thi-ap19:71.2":"caturassam ratham aham; ","thi-ap19:71.3":"Buddhassa pade vandissam, ","thi-ap19:71.4":"lokanathassa tadino. ","thi-ap19:72.1":"‘Supupphitaggam upagamma padapam, ","thi-ap19:72.2":"Eka tuvam titthasi salamule; ","thi-ap19:72.3":"Na capi te dutiyo atthi koci, ","thi-ap19:72.4":"Bale na tvam bhayasi dhuttakanam’. ","thi-ap19:73.1":"‘Satam sahassanipi dhuttakanam, ","thi-ap19:73.2":"Samagata edisaka bhaveyyum; ","thi-ap19:73.3":"Lomam na inje na sampavedhe, ","thi-ap19:73.4":"Kim me tuvam mara karissaseko. ","thi-ap19:74.1":"Esa antaradhayami, ","thi-ap19:74.2":"kucchim va pavisami te; ","thi-ap19:74.3":"Bhamukantarikayampi, ","thi-ap19:74.4":"titthantim mam na dakkhasi. ","thi-ap19:75.1":"Cittasmim vasibhutamhi, ","thi-ap19:75.2":"iddhipada subhavita; ","thi-ap19:75.3":"Sabbabandhanamuttamhi, ","thi-ap19:75.4":"na tam bhayami avuso. ","thi-ap19:76.1":"Sattisulupama kama, ","thi-ap19:76.2":"khandhasam adhikuttana; ","thi-ap19:76.3":"Yam tvam kamaratim brusi, ","thi-ap19:76.4":"arati dani sa mama. ","thi-ap19:77.1":"Sabbattha vihata nandi, ","thi-ap19:77.2":"tamokhandho padalito; ","thi-ap19:77.3":"Evam janahi papima, ","thi-ap19:77.4":"nihato tvamasi antaka’. ","thi-ap19:78.1":"Jino tamhi gune tuttho, ","thi-ap19:78.2":"etadagge thapesi mam; ","thi-ap19:78.3":"Agga iddhimatinanti, ","thi-ap19:78.4":"parisasu vinayako. ","thi-ap19:79.1":"Paricinno maya sattha, ","thi-ap19:79.2":"katam buddhassa sasanam; ","thi-ap19:79.3":"Ohito garuko bharo, ","thi-ap19:79.4":"bhavanettisamuhata. ","thi-ap19:80.1":"Yassatthaya pabbajita, ","thi-ap19:80.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thi-ap19:80.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","thi-ap19:80.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhayo. ","thi-ap19:81.1":"Civaram pindapatanca, ","thi-ap19:81.2":"paccayam sayanasanam; ","thi-ap19:81.3":"Khanena upanamenti, ","thi-ap19:81.4":"sahassani samantato. ","thi-ap19:82.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap19:82.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap19:82.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap19:83.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap19:83.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap19:83.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap19:84.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap19:84.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap19:84.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap19:85.1":"Ittham sudam uppalavanna bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap19:86.1":"Uppalavannatheriyapadanam navamam. "}